author: 08 Liverpool
text: This listenability factor is vital. I must have heard imagine played hundreds of times on the radio. I can’t listen to it anymore. I have roughly 8 Lennon dominant or solo songs, 8 Paul and 4 George (Sorry Ringo)

author: 08 Liverpool
text: So, I have thought of producing a list of my top 10 Beatles songs and top 10 solo songs. This is based on my own view of their meaning to them as artists, overall quality and listenability. Vital when you consider how overplayed some are…

author: 08 Liverpool
text: You can never know all of their output, but you can know a bit and their are always surprise’s #beatles #GetBack

author: 08 Liverpool
text: That is because their music spans an approximate combined 170 years #beatles #GetBack

author: 08 Liverpool
text: So, you don’t listen to Beatles music for over 10 years and then something happens and you reminisce. That something this time is ‘Get Back’. To appreciate the music you probably means need to be interested in their cultural value or perhaps be a historian. #beatles #GetBack
